
# 📋 MovieMap TODO Checklist

A comprehensive, step-by-step checklist to guide the development of the MovieMap project from setup to deployment.

---

## ✅ Project Initialization

- [ ] Create a new GitHub repository
- [ ] Initialize project folder structure
- [ ] Create frontend project with Vite + React
- [ ] Create backend project with Node.js + Express
- [ ] Add `.env` files for frontend and backend
- [ ] Set up `.gitignore` files
- [ ] Add README with project overview

---

## 🛠️ Development Environment Setup

- [ ] Install frontend dependencies (React, Mapbox GL, etc.)
- [ ] Install backend dependencies (Express, pg, dotenv, CORS, Firebase Admin SDK)
- [ ] Configure CORS in Express backend
- [ ] Create `GET /health` route in backend

---

## 🗃️ Database Setup

- [ ] Install and configure PostgreSQL with PostGIS extension
- [ ] Create `locations` table with columns:
  - [ ] id (PK)
  - [ ] title
  - [ ] type (movie/tv)
  - [ ] coordinates (geometry)
  - [ ] trailer_url
  - [ ] imdb_link
- [ ] Create `submissions` table with columns:
  - [ ] All `locations` columns
  - [ ] status (pending/approved/rejected)
- [ ] Create `moderators` table with Firebase UID

---

## 🔐 Authentication

- [ ] Set up Firebase project
- [ ] Enable Firebase Auth with Email/Password or Google Sign-In
- [ ] Integrate Firebase Auth in frontend
- [ ] Verify Firebase ID tokens in backend middleware
- [ ] Restrict admin routes with middleware

---

## 🗺️ Mapbox Frontend

- [ ] Add Mapbox GL JS to React app
- [ ] Load map centered on a default location
- [ ] Create and style pin components
- [ ] Show modal with movie details on pin click
- [ ] Add clustering behavior for overlapping pins

---

## 🔄 API Development

- [ ] Create `GET /locations` to return approved locations
- [ ] Create `POST /submit-location` to accept new submissions
- [ ] Validate submission payload
- [ ] Create `GET /submissions` for admin review
- [ ] Create `PUT /moderate/:id` for approval/rejection

---

## 📝 Community Submission Flow

- [ ] Build a form with fields:
  - [ ] Title
  - [ ] Type
  - [ ] Location name (text)
  - [ ] Map click to select coordinates
  - [ ] Trailer URL
  - [ ] IMDb link
- [ ] Validate inputs in frontend
- [ ] Send POST request to backend on submit

---

## 🛠️ Admin Interface

- [ ] Create `/admin` route
- [ ] Restrict access to authenticated moderators
- [ ] Display list of pending submissions
- [ ] Add "Approve", "Reject", and "Edit" options
- [ ] Submit approval decisions via PUT request

---

## 📱 Mobile Optimization

- [ ] Make Mapbox map responsive
- [ ] Ensure modals work well on small screens
- [ ] Optimize form layout for mobile
- [ ] Ensure admin interface is usable on mobile

---

## 🧪 QA and Testing

- [ ] Test form submissions with invalid/missing data
- [ ] Test modals on all screen sizes
- [ ] Test pin clustering behavior
- [ ] Test API endpoints with Postman or equivalent
- [ ] Test Firebase login and access control

---

## 🚀 Deployment

- [ ] Deploy frontend to Netlify
- [ ] Deploy backend to Render or other platform
- [ ] Set production `.env` variables
- [ ] Test full app in production

---

## 📦 Post-Launch

- [ ] Monitor performance and logs
- [ ] Gather user feedback
- [ ] Plan next iteration (e.g. user accounts, filtering, analytics)

